```
Stack1: [7, 2, 4, 3]   (top = 3)
Stack2: [5, 6, 4]      (top = 4)
```

| Step | s1.pop() | s2.pop() | carry in | val | digit | carry out | head so far |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | 3 | 4 | 0 | 7 | 7 | 0 | 7 |
| 2 | 4 | 6 | 0 | 10 | 0 | 1 | 0 → 7 |
| 3 | 2 | 5 | 1 | 8 | 8 | 0 | 8 → 0 → 7 |
| 4 | 7 | — | 0 | 7 | 7 | 0 | 7 → 8 → 0 → 7 |

**Result: `7 → 8 → 0 → 7`** ✅

